name: Mattres - Full XL, Spring (Bushwick, Brooklyn)
description:
Giving away a Full XL size spring mattress. That means it is 54"x80". A little uncommon but the extra length is very nice. Located near Jefferson Ave and Wyckoff.

NGL this thing is pretty dang old, but free for anyone who can pick it up. Happy to help you carry it downstairs / to your house if you need.

Pictured in a bed-bug protective cover.
